    "In the ABCD model the branching ratio of the LFV τ + µ - mode can be comparable to that of the LFC µ + µ -mode.",
    "Indeed, the decay to same flavour leptons is determined only by the C 10 term, while for ℓ 1 ̸ = ℓ 2 also C 9 contributes."
